comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T17:04:32.096Z",codex-root,Commander 15 requires Node >=22.12; ESLint 10.7 requires >=22.13 on the Node 22 line.
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T17:04:32.096Z",codex-root,TypeScript 7.0.2 is intentionally deferred because @typescript-eslint 8.64.0 declares TypeScript <6.1.0.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T17:04:32.096Z",codex-root,@types/node should match the supported runtime line rather than always follow the registry latest major.
files[2]{path,scope,note}:
  package.json,project,decision implementation
  tsconfig.json,project,explicit runtime type contract
tests[2]{command,scope,note}:
  bun run lint,project,ESLint compatibility
  bun run typecheck,project,TypeScript compatibility
docs[1]{path,scope,note}:
  docs/DEVELOPMENT.md,project,toolchain policy
body: "Adopt Bun 1.3.11, Node >=22.13, Commander 15, ESLint 10, Vitest 4, and TypeScript 6.0.3. Do not adopt TypeScript 7 until TypeScript-ESLint expands its peer range beyond <6.1.0; retain @types/node 22 to model the supported Node line rather than unrelated Node 26 APIs."
